{"tid":1822751,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【代友開po】我係黃狗，我知道d狗都唔知道既野","createTime":"2020-01-13T06:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T05:54:14.000Z","uid":118941,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"92cd123e1482a1b4b878d32eabf085be732481b1","tid":1822751,"uid":118941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"咁多條浮尸，其實有小部分係我地班狗。<br />\n我唔知邊個做，可能係手足做，都可能係高層狗為滅聲。<br />\n但係上頭為左唔比下面既人亂同減低士氣，全部都話係無可疑全部唔準查，咁好彩有伙計發現係識既都會被滅聲。所以我覺得高層為滅聲既機會係大好多。<br />\n而最慘既係，個一班弱智既毅進仔信到十足，覺得全部都係暴徒抵死而真係唔查落去。<br />\n<br />\n信就信，唔信就算。<br />\n而且我呢個po其實係主要比mon po 既伙計睇，<br />\n唔好做condom啦傻仔。"},{"pid":"7bec44eae995174231bb11eab2f6454e4401a0a4","tid":1822751,"uid":287329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T12:05:31.000Z","msg":"你代朋友po架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2c51bbe3cf819ace66216ae669f32ded5c339e","tid":1822751,"uid":118941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bec44eae995174231bb11eab2f6454e4401a0a4","tid":1822751,"uid":287329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T12:05:31.000Z","msg":"你代朋友po架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T17:00:53.000Z","msg":"係呀，我代朋友po架咋"},{"pid":"3ed5a263f7c4029724d2d8d7882d5ebbcf5742d5","tid":1822751,"uid":65178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T17:16:51.000Z","msg":"冇興趣知真假 總之衷心希望黑警死全家 死無全屍 最好死曬 講完"},{"pid":"de414c4871cba7484fe469549ed3395a73145ec3","tid":1822751,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T17:37:14.000Z","msg":"有警察甩條毛都講到甩個頭咁濟，咁好機會警謊唔乘機利用？太公報唔頭版&quot;暴徒殺警&quot;大大隻字？你真係on9到極點！"},{"pid":"5c9b76ff6c201670e78717f75d93f0d8cd245052","tid":1822751,"uid":9412,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"浮尸<br />\nPOST已完"},{"pid":"005ed6ba7d6ea6fecd66cd2771bfd41a5e2bea35","tid":1822751,"uid":118941,"like